msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||171||||4"
msgid "You have issues on both sides of things...\nbut with my help, we'll hammer them out in no time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||172||||4"
msgid "That concludes today's RIZAP Challenge.\nNicely done!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||173||||4"
msgid "Wow, Kiryu-san!\nYou've done every single RIZAP Challenge!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||174||||4"
msgid "Huh. So that was the last one?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||175||||4"
msgid "Yes, the 12th and final challenge is complete!\nNow let's see how far you've come!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||176||||4"
msgid "So what did you think of RIZAP?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||177||||4"
msgid "I'm glad I decided to join.\nI didn't expect such a personal touch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||178||||4"
msgid "I learned a lot about my diet, too.\nYou weren't kidding about being committed to results."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||179||||4"
msgid "It's nice to hear such high praise!\nMore importantly, today marks your RIZAP graduation!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||180||||4"
msgid "However, Kiryu-san! You can re-enroll\nas a member whenever you'd like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||181||||4"
msgid "Come talk to me if you're feeling out of shape!\nWe can start from the very beginning again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||182||||4"
msgid "Hopefully it doesn't come to that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||183||||4"
msgid "Don't be a stranger, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||184||||4"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san! Are you looking\nto re-enroll in the RIZAP program?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||185||||4"
msgid "I am..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||186||||4"
msgid "I'm feeling kinda rusty, to be honest.\nGet me back on the plan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||187||||4"
msgid "A wonderful decision!\nI'll process your membership right away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||188||||4"
msgid "Please talk to me when you want to train!\nI'll help you get the body you've always dreamed of!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||189||||4"
msgid "(I don't have enough money...\nMaybe I should come back later.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||190||||4"
msgid "Actually, I was just checking in.\nSorry to bother you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||speech_list_sub_a25||table||191||||4"
msgid "It's no problem.\nJust come again if you ever want to train!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||0||||4"
msgid "Hold the freakin' phone!\nIs that you, Kiryu-san!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||1||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||2||||4"
msgid "Wowee! It really <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> you!\nIt's been ages, man!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||3||||4"
msgid "Wait..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||4||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||6||||4"
msgid "C'mon, bro!\nYou can't have forgotten <font_kind=yakuza_italic>me</font_kind>!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||7||||4"
msgid "It's me, Sodachi! So, da, chi!\nY'know, the head honcho of the Sodachi Dojo!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||8||||4"
msgid "Sodachi? Sodachi..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||9||||4"
msgid "Ah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||10||||4"
msgid "<font_kind=yakuza_italic>Yeah</font_kind>!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||11||||4"
msgid "I have no idea who you are."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||12||||4"
msgid "God, you're the worst! Don't you remember\nour epic flurry of fists back at the arena?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||13||||4"
msgid "It <font_kind=yakuza_italic>was</font_kind> just one time, though.\nCan't really blame you for forgetting..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||14||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I wish I remembered."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||15||||4"
msgid "No worries!\nI just gotta give you a little reminder!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||16||||4"
msgid "Folks 'round here call me Yasuo Sodachi.\nI used to head up the Sodachi Dojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||17||||4"
msgid "I was real close to your friend\nSaejima-san back in the good ol' days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||18||||4"
msgid "Oh, you know Saejima?\nLet's start over. It's good to meet you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||19||||4"
msgid "I'm not surprised you ran a dojo.\nThose muscles are incredible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||20||||4"
msgid "Ain't they the best?\nBut y'know, I actually closed the dojo down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||21||||4"
msgid "I still miss the ol' stomping grounds...\nI've got tons of memories of Saejima-san there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||22||||4"
msgid "That's too bad.\nDid... something happen to make you close?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||23||||4"
msgid "Oh not at all, unless you count the surging\nland prices! It was high time to sell, baby!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||25||||4"
msgid "I wasn't keen on doing it, but at that price?\nSometimes you gotta make sacrifices."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||26||||4"
msgid "And now thanks to a little investment I made\nhere at RIZAP, I've got this killer bod!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||27||||4"
msgid "They really <font_kind=yakuza_italic>are</font_kind> good at getting results!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||28||||4"
msgid "Wait, you got stronger <font_kind=yakuza_italic>here</font_kind> of all places?\nWouldn't running a dojo keep you in shape?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||29||||4"
msgid "Not at all! I might've been the master,\nbut I was kind of a piss-poor fighter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||30||||4"
msgid "I gotta say though, I made the right call.\nThis gym's way better than our dingy dojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||31||||4"
msgid "And look what it did to my body!\nI'm the shining example of buffness!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||32||||4"
msgid "Right. Well, I've gotta go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||33||||4"
msgid "But Kiryu-san! Listen to me!\nG-G-Get your ass back here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||34||||4"
msgid "Huh? What do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||35||||4"
msgid "So scary...!\nC'mon Sodachi, you can do this... And go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||36||||4"
msgid "Hey there, Kiryu-san! Wait... <font_kind=yakuza_italic>Kiryu</font_kind>!\nPlease... Er, I wanna lock fists with you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||37||||4"
msgid "You want a fight?\nWith me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||38||||4"
msgid "Damn skippy! I've looked up to strong dudes\nlike you and Saejima-san my whole life!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||39||||4"
msgid "I wanna get as strong as you guys someday...\nThen beat you! That's my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||40||||4"
msgid "I'd given up on that dream for years...\nBut things're different now that I'm a beefcake!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||41||||4"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||42||||4"
msgid "My power's outta control compared to my past self!\nI'm really itching to put it to the test."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||43||||4"
msgid "I've gotta see how close I am to\nthe one and only Kazuma Kiryu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||44||||4"
msgid "Hey, wait up!\nDon't leave!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||45||||4"
msgid "What a pain in the ass.\nI'm sorry, but I don't have time for this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||46||||4"
msgid "Whatever, man!\nIn that case, I'll have to make the first move!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||47||||4"
msgid "No freaking way...\nI don't stand a chance against <font_kind=yakuza_italic>you</font_kind>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||48||||4"
msgid "You're strong, but your footwork needs practice.\nRight now you're just wasting your strength."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||49||||4"
msgid "I know... My dojo training's made me\nwell-versed in all that technical stuff."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||50||||4"
msgid "But... even though I know what to do,\nmy body just ain't quick enough to do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||51||||4"
msgid "Some pickle this is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||52||||4"
msgid "You should keep practicing.\nExperience is the only way to improve."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||53||||4"
msgid "Yeah, you're right...\nAh, I've got it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||54||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! I'm gonna practice extra hard\nso I can make use of these sweet muscles!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||55||||4"
msgid "And once I'm done, we're gonna tussle again!\nI hope you're ready for more!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||56||||4"
msgid "Yeah...\nWait, what? We're gonna fight <font_kind=yakuza_italic>again</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||57||||4"
msgid "Of course we are! Beating you's the only way\nto prove I've got the fighting skills to fighting thrill!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||58||||4"
msgid "If I can do that, and show the world\nthe hurt I'm packing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||59||||4"
msgid "I'll be able to make a super dojo\nand get stupidly rich!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||60||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna make it rain on these Kamurocho civvies!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||62||||4"
msgid "Anyways, I'll be training till next time!\nSeeya later, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||63||||4"
msgid "What a mess.\nHow do I always get wrapped up in this stuff...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||64||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||65||||4"
msgid "I've tightened up my stance a bit!\nHow 'bout we go another round?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||66||||4"
msgid "I'm really starting to get good!\nHow 'bout we go another round?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||67||||4"
msgid "My body's never been this pumped up!\nHow 'bout we go another round?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||68||||4"
msgid "I can't right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||69||||4"
msgid "Huh? C'mon, man!\nAnyway, lemme know if you change your mind!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||70||||4"
msgid "Ah, Kiryu-san!\nDo you feel like fighting me now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||71||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll take you on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||72||||4"
msgid "Sweet!\nThanks a ton!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||73||||4"
msgid "Now, then...\nDieee, Kiryuuu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||74||||4"
msgid "Dammittt... I lost again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||75||||4"
msgid "You're definitely stronger than last time, though.\nThat's progress."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||76||||4"
msgid "You mean it!? All right, then!\nThis isn't the last you see of me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||77||||4"
msgid "No way... I beat Kiryu-san!\nI really did it! Yay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||78||||4"
msgid "I underestimated you.\nTurns out you're pretty tough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||79||||4"
msgid "No way were you in tip-top form today,\nbut it doesn't matter. A win's a win in my book!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||80||||4"
msgid "And as the winner of our match,\nlet me say one thing, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||81||||4"
msgid "Your luck ran out today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||82||||4"
msgid "Make sure you're pumped up next time, okay?\nBye now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||83||||4"
msgid "Dammit, I should never have underestimated him.\nHow embarrassing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||84||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||85||||4"
msgid "It's from Sodachi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||86||||4"
msgid "How did he get my contact info...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||87||||4"
msgid "Whatever. I'll head over to the park\nand humor him when I have some time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||88||||4"
msgid "Yo, Kiryu-san!\nThanks for coming all the way out here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||89||||4"
msgid "It's nothing.\nWell? What do you want?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||90||||4"
msgid "Hold up, man!\nDidn't you read my freakin' email!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||91||||4"
msgid "Today's the day we settle this.\nJust me... and you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||92||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||93||||4"
msgid "Well, thanks to all my training at RIZAP,\nI've finally unlocked my true potential."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||94||||4"
msgid "Anything I imagine, I can make into reality.\nThis is, so to speak, my final form!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||95||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||96||||4"
msgid "So today, I'm gonna whoop you, Kiryu-san!\nThe world's gonna see how tough I am!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||97||||4"
msgid "Nobody'll be able to deny my ability once\nI've taken down the toughest dude in the world!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||98||||4"
msgid "My new gym's gonna skyrocket to the top!\nOh, and I'll make fat stacks off my fighting book, too!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||100||||4"
msgid "Some plan you have there.\nI'd rather you didn't use my name, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||101||||4"
msgid "I won't, man.\n<font_kind=yakuza_italic>If</font_kind> you can beat me, that is!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||102||||4"
msgid "Now let's get moving.\nThis is our last dance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||103||||4"
msgid "Dieee, Kazuma Kiryuuu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||104||||4"
msgid "Dammit, I took him too lightly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||105||||4"
msgid "I-I actually won!\nI'm the king of the world!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||106||||4"
msgid "Now that I've laid a whooping on <font_kind=yakuza_italic>the</font_kind> Kazuma Kiryu,\nmy gym empire's just a hop and a skip away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||107||||4"
msgid "Tch..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||108||||4"
msgid "Too bad, Kiryu-san. But I will say,\nit's only 'cause of you that I got this strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||109||||4"
msgid "That's why I'll let you redeem yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||110||||4"
msgid "Come back if you think you can beat me in\na rematch. I'll take you on as much as you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||111||||4"
msgid "I've already planned out the fight, though.\nYou're gonna fail just as hard as you did this time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||112||||4"
msgid "Keep coming my way if you wanna die, Kiryu-san!\nJust kidding!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||114||||4"
msgid "(This is humiliating... but he <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> strong.\nI should put my head down and try again.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||115||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!\nHere for another smackdown?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||116||||4"
msgid "I can't let this end like that.\nThis time, it's going to be different."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||117||||4"
msgid "What, you <font_kind=yakuza_italic>really</font_kind> think you can beat me?\nWell now's your chance to prove it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||118||||4"
msgid "You're dead meattt, Kiryuuu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||119||||4"
msgid "I lost..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||120||||4"
msgid "You're a lot stronger, Sodachi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||121||||4"
msgid "Can't disagree with that.\nBut the legendary Kiryu's still a cut above."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||122||||4"
msgid "I only got this strong thanks to you, man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||123||||4"
msgid "My admiration toward you, my desire to beat you...\nThose were the best motivators a guy could ask for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||124||||4"
msgid "That's what helped me get through my training.\nI've really gotta thank you for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||125||||4"
msgid "All I did was smack you around a few times.\nYour hard work is what really made you stronger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||126||||4"
msgid "You should be proud."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||127||||4"
msgid "Y-You think? Yeah, you're right!\nI totally gave it my all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||129||||4"
msgid "But no matter how much effort I put in,\nmy appreciation for you remains unchanged."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||130||||4"
msgid "If there's ever anything I can do for you,\ndon't hesitate to give me a ring!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||131||||4"
msgid "All right. Will do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||132||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||133||||4"
msgid "Who's that...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||134||||4"
msgid "Is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||135||||4"
msgid "Nah, nah, it's nothing! Just some guy\nwho looked like a hidden video game boss!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||136||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||137||||4"
msgid "I'm sure it's nothing to get worked up over.\nCan't judge a book by its cover, after all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||138||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||139||||4"
msgid "Anyways, I should be outta here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||140||||4"
msgid "I might've lost <font_kind=yakuza_italic>this</font_kind> time, but I'm gonna keep\ntraining so I can get to your level, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||141||||4"
msgid "Gimme another fight someday, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||142||||4"
msgid "Heh... If I feel like it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||143||||4"
msgid "Good enough! Later!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||144||||4"
msgid "Hmph."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||speech_list_sub_a26||table||145||||4"
msgid "Kazuma Kiryu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||0||||4"
msgid "That's enough of this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||1||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry. I just..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||2||||4"
msgid "You'll never amount to anything with that attitude.\nDon't you understand?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||3||||4"
msgid "I-I do. I just wanted to see\nhim one last time before I left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||5||||4"
msgid "How are you ever going to survive in Tokyo like this?\nIt's a harsh world up there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||6||||4"
msgid "Idol life isn't all just fun and games!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||7||||4"
msgid "So, that girl wants to be an idol?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||8||||4"
msgid "B-But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||9||||4"
msgid "If you're serious about pursuing this career path,\nyou'll need to leave this town, and him, behind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||10||||4"
msgid "Idols aren't allowed to be in love."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||12||||4"
msgid "I suggest you heed my warning."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||13||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||15||||4"
msgid "You're trying to become an idol, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||16||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||17||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I didn't mean to eavesdrop on you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||18||||4"
msgid "I'm such a disgrace, aren't I?\nI shouldn't be crying in public like this..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||19||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||20||||4"
msgid "Cheer up, kid. I'll see you around."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||22||||4"
msgid "No, I really appreciate the offer.\n I think it'll help talking to someone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||23||||4"
msgid "Hey, are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||25||||4"
msgid "Why don't you talk to me for a bit?\nIt'll be better for you than crying here all alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||26||||4"
msgid "I don't want to force you, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||28||||4"
msgid "My name is Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||29||||4"
msgid "You're from Tokyo, right, Kiryu-san?\nI didn't think you'd be so... kind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||30||||4"
msgid "Anyone would be worried about\na girl your age crying in the street."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||31||||4"
msgid "Anyway, feel free to tell me what's bothering you.\nThat was some argument you were having."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||32||||4"
msgid "That woman from earlier is from a production firm\nbased up in Tokyo. She's my manager, Endo-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||33||||4"
msgid "Endo seemed really upset with you for some reason."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||34||||4"
msgid "Yeah, there's a pretty big rule I'm breaking...\nOnce you become an idol, dating's off-limits."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||35||||4"
msgid "That's why she was yelling at me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||36||||4"
msgid "Off-limits, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||37||||4"
msgid "What happened is, I had finally had a breakout\nmoment in an audition, and got reassigned to Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||38||||4"
msgid "But, that's when I realized something: I have feelings\nfor an old childhood friend and senpai of mine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||39||||4"
msgid "Even though I was taking lessons about being an idol,\nthe thought of leaving him worried me to no end."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||40||||4"
msgid "That's understandable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||41||||4"
msgid "He's been so supportive about me realizing my\ndream, though. He was there when nobody else was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||42||||4"
msgid "Now that I think about it, he was the first person\nI told about me moving to Tokyo after the audition, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||44||||4"
msgid "Even when my parents and the other adults refused\nto support me, he was there, cheering me on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||45||||4"
msgid "Sounds pretty special."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||46||||4"
msgid "He is. That's why I want to make sure he knows\nhow I feel before I leave for Tokyo forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||47||||4"
msgid "If he accepts me... I think I'm going to stay here.\nI won't know his answer until I tell him, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||48||||4"
msgid "I guess it's no surprise your manager is upset."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||49||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I know it's dumb."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||50||||4"
msgid "This is supposed to be my make-or-break moment\nas an idol, but my stupid emotions are in the way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||51||||4"
msgid "Maybe... Maybe I should just go to Tokyo.\nCan I really ignore my feelings like that...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||52||||4"
msgid "No matter what, you should go tell him how you feel.\nAt least that's what I would do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||53||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||54||||4"
msgid "If you don't, you'll always wonder what would\nhave happened if you hadn't run away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||55||||4"
msgid "That's how it goes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||56||||4"
msgid "Oh. I hadn't thought of it like that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||57||||4"
msgid "It's better if you don't go see him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||58||||4"
msgid "If you give up on your idol dream now,\nall the support he gave you will have been for nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||59||||4"
msgid "But if I go to Tokyo now, who knows if\nI'll ever be able to see him again..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||60||||4"
msgid "You can either become an idol, or stay\nwith this guy. The choice is yours."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||61||||4"
msgid "I-I guess you're right about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||62||||4"
msgid "Why don't I help you forget about him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||63||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||64||||4"
msgid "A rebound is always a quick fix for a broken heart.\nOlder men tend to be more experienced, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||65||||4"
msgid "Um... You can't be serious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||66||||4"
msgid "I thought you were nice for listening to me,\nbut now your real intentions come to light."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||67||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||68||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||69||||4"
msgid "It was a joke."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||70||||4"
msgid "Oh, good! Funny joke, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||71||||4"
msgid "...Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||72||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||73||||4"
msgid "Anyway, what are you going to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||74||||4"
msgid "Um, I think I'm going to go see him.\nI can't leave for Tokyo without saying how I feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||75||||4"
msgid "Right. I can't say I'm surprised."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||76||||4"
msgid "When people are troubled by something, they usually\njust need to look for the answer within themselves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||77||||4"
msgid "Oh. So that's why you decided to talk to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||78||||4"
msgid "Thank you, Kiryu-san. I feel a little bit\nbetter now that I've talked to you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||79||||4"
msgid "It was nothing. Well, I should be going.\nAre you going to be okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||80||||4"
msgid "Yes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||81||||4"
msgid "What's going on, Misa? Aren't you going\nto tell that senpai of yours how you feel?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||82||||4"
msgid "I tried, but I got kinda nervous...\nSorry, but can you give me some more time?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||83||||4"
msgid "Sure. I wasn't trying to rush you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||84||||4"
msgid "Hm? Is that... Misa? So the guy\nmust be the one she mentioned earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||85||||4"
msgid "Um, well, there's something\nI really need to talk to you about!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||86||||4"
msgid "What's going on, Misa? I'm all ears."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||87||||4"
msgid "Um, do you remember how I told you my dream\nof becoming an idol back in middle school, senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||88||||4"
msgid "Yeah, of course I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||89||||4"
msgid "It was after you saw Haruka Sawamura's\nlast concert on TV. That was what inspired you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||90||||4"
msgid "So Misa wants to be an idol now\nbecause of Haruka...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||91||||4"
msgid "Back then, everyone made fun of me and\ncalled me names. You were different, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||92||||4"
msgid "You've supported me nonstop since then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||94||||4"
msgid "The truth is, um... from that day forward, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||95||||4"
msgid "It would be rude of me to keep listening to this.\nI should get out of here before they notice me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||96||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||97||||4"
msgid "Well, well! Look what we got here!\nY'guys're real cute, y'know?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||98||||4"
msgid "This ain't no place t'be gettin'\nall lovey-dovey like that, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||99||||4"
msgid "U-Uh, excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||100||||4"
msgid "Hey, we're in the middle of something! Go away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||101||||4"
msgid "Y'really got the balls t'be tellin' us off?\nDon't y'know yer in a public place? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||102||||4"
msgid "It looks like I might need to get involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||103||||4"
msgid "Hey bro, we don't got business with ya.\nWe're way more into this li'l lady over here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||104||||4"
msgid "'At's right! Yer in our way, brat! Y'better get\nlost before we gotta lay the beatdown on ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||105||||4"
msgid "Okay! Please don't hurt me...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||106||||4"
msgid "Huh? S-Senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||107||||4"
msgid "(Some senpai he is.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||108||||4"
msgid "Look, Misa. These guys probably aren't so bad, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||109||||4"
msgid "Plus, I've got entrance exams coming up.\nI can't be getting hurt now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||110||||4"
msgid "W-Wait, what...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||111||||4"
msgid "I'm really sorry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||112||||4"
msgid "Senpai! Please, don't leave me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||113||||4"
msgid "Jus' forget about him, li'l lady.\nYer boyfriend abandoned ya here, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||114||||4"
msgid "How 'bout y'have some fun with us instead?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||115||||4"
msgid "I said, no! You guys are\nnothing but a bunch of thugs!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||116||||4"
msgid "Huh? What're y'lookin' at, gramps?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||117||||4"
msgid "This ain't any o' yer business!\nGet lost, ya old fuck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||118||||4"
msgid "This actually isn't any of <font_kind=yakuza_italic>your</font_kind> business.\nYou interrupted a tender moment here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||119||||4"
msgid "If you want to lay your hands on the girl,\nyou're going to have to go through me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||120||||4"
msgid "Who the hell's this shit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||121||||4"
msgid "Ugh, whatever. We're gonna make ya\nregret gettin' in our way! C'mon!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||122||||4"
msgid "H-Hold on a sec, old man! Look,\nwe're only doin' this 'cause someone asked us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||123||||4"
msgid "I think that's enough.\nYou've served your purpose."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||124||||4"
msgid "Endo-san? Wait, what's going on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||125||||4"
msgid "That woman... She's Misa's manager, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||126||||4"
msgid "I'm the one who hired these men. I wanted\nto test how devoted your senpai is to you, Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||127||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||128||||4"
msgid "As I expected, he instead showed us the true cowardice\nin his heart. Has that cured your lovesickness, Misa?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||129||||4"
msgid "Endo-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||130||||4"
msgid "I haven't actually started packing for Tokyo yet.\nI should probably go do that, huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||131||||4"
msgid "Yes. It's for the best."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||133||||4"
msgid "Misa!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||134||||4"
msgid "You've done quite enough already... Kazuma Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||135||||4"
msgid "What? You know who I am?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||136||||4"
msgid "Of course I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||137||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the industry knows that face of yours.\nYou're the yakuza who forced Haruka into retirement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||138||||4"
msgid "I don't care why you're down here in Onomichi,\nbut I need you to stop trying to help Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||139||||4"
msgid "Her conscience needs to be clear when she\nheads up to Tokyo. Isn't that right, senpai?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||140||||4"
msgid "What? I don't get it. You were in on this scheme, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||141||||4"
msgid "Yes. I'm actually the one who came up\nwith the idea to begin with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||142||||4"
msgid "Those other guys are classmates of mine.\nAll Endo-san did was agree to follow along."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||143||||4"
msgid "Man, y'really put us through the ringer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||144||||4"
msgid "Sorry about that, you guys. I'll buy you\ndinner to make up for it, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||145||||4"
msgid "Sure, sure. See ya later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||146||||4"
msgid "Care to explain what's going on here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||147||||4"
msgid "I don't know if this is much of an explanation,\nbut I've been there for Misa every step of the way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||148||||4"
msgid "I know just how hard she's had to work\nto get to where she is today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||149||||4"
msgid "That's why... That's why she needs to focus on\nbeing an idol instead of confessing to a chump like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||150||||4"
msgid "He's had feelings for Misa for many years now.\nSince far before she realized how she felt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||151||||4"
msgid "So this was all for Misa, then.\nThat's why you're pulling yourself away from her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||152||||4"
msgid "If I stop her from pursuing her dream of stardom,\nI'd never be able to forgive myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||153||||4"
msgid "Even if Misa and I ended up together,\nI'm sure that would always weigh heavy on my mind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||155||||4"
msgid "You know, when Endo-san told me the other day how\nMisa felt about me, I was honestly over the moon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||156||||4"
msgid "But that's exactly why I didn't think I'd be able to trick\nher like this. I can't stand the thought of hurting her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||157||||4"
msgid "So this was all for her sake..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||158||||4"
msgid "If Misa abandons her feelings for me, she'll be able to\npush onward toward her dream without any regrets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||159||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I don't care how she thinks of me now.\nI'd do whatever it takes for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||161||||4"
msgid "Even for someone you love,\nthat's not an easy path to walk."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||162||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, was it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||163||||4"
msgid "If you ever see Misa around town,\ncould you not tell her about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||164||||4"
msgid "To be perfectly honest, I'd much rather\nlet her know what's going on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||165||||4"
msgid "But I'm just an outsider. It's not\nreally my place to say anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||166||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much. Goodbye, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||167||||4"
msgid "I appreciate this, Kiryu-san.\nLet me show my gratitude."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||168||||4"
msgid "Is this supposed to keep me quiet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||169||||4"
msgid "It's a simple thank-you gift."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||170||||4"
msgid "You know, even though you're a famous yakuza,\nyou actually turned out to be quite understanding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||171||||4"
msgid "Huh. You're kinder than you look, too.\nAnyway, take good care of Misa."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||172||||4"
msgid "I will."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||173||||4"
msgid "Speaking of which, where did Misa run off to?\nShe seemed pretty shocked earlier."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||174||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||175||||4"
msgid "Misa? How long have you been there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||176||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||177||||4"
msgid "I... I didn't hear anything, promise!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||178||||4"
msgid "Then why did you run away?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||179||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||180||||4"
msgid "I know you're probably confused after hearing all that.\nI'm sure it's hard to know everyone is deceiving you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||181||||4"
msgid "But I need you to listen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||182||||4"
msgid "Pretend like you didn't hear any of that. Go to Tokyo,\nand succeed. That's what Endo and your senpai want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||183||||4"
msgid "So you're taking their side, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||184||||4"
msgid "I guess I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||185||||4"
msgid "You should be a track star instead of an idol.\nIt's damn impressive how fast you can run."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||186||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||187||||4"
msgid "Plus if you did that, there wouldn't be\nany problem with you dating your senpai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||188||||4"
msgid "That's a dumb joke..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||190||||4"
msgid "Love is more important than entertainment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||191||||4"
msgid "That senpai you admire so much is a great guy.\nPeople aren't really like that up in Tokyo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||192||||4"
msgid "But if I stay here, do you think he'll really be happy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||193||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||194||||4"
msgid "You heard what he was saying earlier, Kiryu-san.\nHe'd regret holding me back from my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||195||||4"
msgid "If I want to keep him happy and in love with me,\nleaving for Tokyo is my only option."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||196||||4"
msgid "You may be right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||197||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||198||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||199||||4"
msgid "Well, I never would have fallen for senpai if he was the\nkind of guy who'd abandon me to some random thugs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||201||||4"
msgid "I saw right through him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||202||||4"
msgid "I knew something was up, so I pretended\nto run off and hid nearby to watch."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||203||||4"
msgid "After all, idols have to be good at acting, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||204||||4"
msgid "I'm so happy, though. I had no idea he was\nso invested in making sure I achieved my dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||205||||4"
msgid "I... I won't let him down.\nI'm going to give this all I've got."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||206||||4"
msgid "Good. I'm sure your senpai will be happy to hear that.\nHe should be able to keep his distance in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||207||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||208||||4"
msgid "Idols aren't allowed to be in love, remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||209||||4"
msgid "Um... do you think he'll still be waiting for me\nwhen I'm done with everything I want to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||210||||4"
msgid "Him? He'd wait even if you told him not to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||211||||4"
msgid "I hope you're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||212||||4"
msgid "Well, good luck, Misa. I'll be rooting for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||214||||4"
msgid "Um, Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||215||||4"
msgid "Becoming an idol's only the first part of my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||216||||4"
msgid "To be honest, there's one more thing I want\nto do in the entertainment industry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||217||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||218||||4"
msgid "I want to perform in a crowded dome full of\nloving fans. That's where I'll announce my retirement."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||219||||4"
msgid "Everyone in the audience and watching on TV will be\nso surprised. I'll run off the stage, and be gone forever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||220||||4"
msgid "Just like Haruka-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||221||||4"
msgid "I hope you're joking."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||222||||4"
msgid "So, what do you think? You have firsthand\nexperience with that, right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||223||||4"
msgid "Don't do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||224||||4"
msgid "It'll be nothing but trouble for those around you.\nThe media seriously never lets up..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||225||||4"
msgid "It's a harsh world out there, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||226||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||227||||4"
msgid "I'll have to do my best."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||228||||4"
msgid "Um... Kiryu-san, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||229||||4"
msgid "Hm? Oh, you're the guy Misa is in love with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||230||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I want to thank you\nfor everything you did for her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||231||||4"
msgid "Have you spoken to her since then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||232||||4"
msgid "I haven't. She already knows how I feel,\nand I already know how she feels about me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||233||||4"
msgid "Someday soon she'll be on TV and in magazines.\nI can't wait to see what she makes of herself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||234||||4"
msgid "Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||235||||4"
msgid "Though... even though I'm trying to act cool,\nI can't help but wonder if I made the right decision."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||236||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't have time to worry if I was still\nwith the team, but I already retired."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||237||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh. What kind of team were you on?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||238||||4"
msgid "Baseball. The team wasn't the greatest around,\nbut I was the captain for a few years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||239||||4"
msgid "Oh? I'm actually on a baseball team myself.\nIt's just a little local one, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||240||||4"
msgid "If you'd like, maybe you could come play\non our team between classes sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||241||||4"
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||242||||4"
msgid "It'll help you stop worrying so much. Besides,\nanyone with experience is welcome on our team."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||243||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much! In that case,\nI might just take you up on that offer."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||244||||4"
msgid "My name is Kase. I can't wait to\nstart playing games together, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||speech_list_sub_b01||table||245||||4"
msgid "Same to you, Kase-senpai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||0||||4"
msgid "Mie-san, you can't let them trick you like this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||1||||4"
msgid "Y'got it all wrong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||2||||4"
msgid "Jus' don't worry about it.\nI'll be fine, really."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||3||||4"
msgid "That's what they want you to think, Mie-san!\nTrust me, those Munan Chohept Onast guys are bad news!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||4||||4"
msgid "Munan Chohept?\nWhat are they talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||5||||4"
msgid "Everyone over there's jus' so nice, though!\nYou'll see if ya come down to the facility."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||6||||4"
msgid "You'd make a great Friend, y'know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||7||||4"
msgid "They're gonna bleed you dry, Mie-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||8||||4"
msgid "They've told you about the donations, right?\nHow that's the only way to salvation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||9||||4"
msgid "It's called titherance! We've gotta\nshow our devotion to the divine savior."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||10||||4"
msgid "I don't care <font_kind=yakuza_italic>what</font_kind> it's called!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||11||||4"
msgid "Listen to me. You can't keep going back there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||13||||4"
msgid "Hands off, old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||14||||4"
msgid "E-Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||15||||4"
msgid "S-Sorry, I lost my temper for a second."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||16||||4"
msgid "That's enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||17||||4"
msgid "Y'wouldn't get mad so easily\nif you jus' had a little faith."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||18||||4"
msgid "Wait, Mie-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||19||||4"
msgid "You came on a little strong there.\nI assume you have your reasons?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||20||||4"
msgid "Um, who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||21||||4"
msgid "I'm just passing by. I'm actually not\nfrom around here. The name's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||22||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||23||||4"
msgid "Um, if it's all right with you, d-do you think\nyou can hear me out? I can't promise it'll be quick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||24||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I'm busy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||25||||4"
msgid "Sure, I'll listen.\nYou look pretty drained, old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||26||||4"
msgid "Munan Chohept Onast is to blame for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||27||||4"
msgid "What exactly is this Munan thing anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||28||||4"
msgid "They're a terrible cult that's been\naround for over 30 years now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||29||||4"
msgid "Lately they've left the big cities\nfor small towns like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||30||||4"
msgid "Elderly retirees with no relatives\nare their primary targets."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||31||||4"
msgid "Naturally, they're only after their money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||32||||4"
msgid "Which brings us to the woman from earlier.\nShe's wrapped up with this cult now, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||33||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Her name is Mie-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||34||||4"
msgid "I only just moved here a couple of months ago,\nbut she's shown me nothing but kindness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||35||||4"
msgid "Talking to Mie-san takes me back to when\nI was still chasin' skirts around town..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||37||||4"
msgid "But she's changed.\nI can't believe she'd fall for their lies!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||38||||4"
msgid "And you're absolutely sure this religion is a scam?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||39||||4"
msgid "There's no doubt in my mind, yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||40||||4"
msgid "This cult transforms its followers into thoughtless drones.\nThey make them donate every last yen they have, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||41||||4"
msgid "That's terrible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||42||||4"
msgid "As for Mie-san, her husband died recently\nafter many great years in her care."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||43||||4"
msgid "And those bastards took advantage\nof her at her most vulnerable."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||44||||4"
msgid "She won't listen to a word I say, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||45||||4"
msgid "Others from around town have joined the cult as well.\nThey all think it's the most wonderful thing in the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||46||||4"
msgid "At the very least, I want to save Mie-san.\nI can't bear to watch her throw her life away like this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||47||||4"
msgid "Have you gone to the police?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||48||||4"
msgid "They wouldn't listen to me, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||49||||4"
msgid "The cops won't lift a finger until\nthey can have some hard evidence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||50||||4"
msgid "But it'll be too late by then!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||52||||4"
msgid "Um, I hesitate to ask this of you...\nWe only just met, after all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||53||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||54||||4"
msgid "Please, will you come over to the\nMunan Chohept Onast facility with me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||55||||4"
msgid "We should be able to sneak in\nif we pretend we want to join."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||56||||4"
msgid "I'd never be able to do it alone at my age. \nBut... I can't just abandon Mie-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||57||||4"
msgid "I'll drag her out kicking and screaming if I have to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||58||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I'm a little busy right now.\nMaybe some other time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||59||||4"
msgid "Yeah, let's do it. I won't let you rush in there\nalone and risk getting yourself hurt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||60||||4"
msgid "Thank you, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||61||||4"
msgid "So, where is their headquarters?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||62||||4"
msgid "It's down by the coast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||63||||4"
msgid "It's over by the train tracks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||64||||4"
msgid "There should be some young ladies passing out\nflyers out front. You'll know when you see it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||65||||4"
msgid "All right. Shall we?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||66||||4"
msgid "Yeah. We should head over separately, though.\nThey're more likely to take us in if we're alone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||67||||4"
msgid "Does that sound good?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||68||||4"
msgid "Are you sure about this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||69||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I know how they operate.\nLonely-looking people are easy prey for them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||71||||4"
msgid "Anyway, I'll head over first to look for Mie-san.\nI'll see you there soon, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||72||||4"
msgid "Right, see you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||73||||4"
msgid "Goodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||74||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san! Do you have time\nto listen to my story right now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||75||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san. Will you accompany me\nto the Munan Chohept headquarters?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||76||||4"
msgid "Embrace the salvation of this\nheavenly body we call Earth!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||77||||4"
msgid "The light of the world shall permeate your soul!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||78||||4"
msgid "(Those girls are handing out flyers...\nThis must be that cult's headquarters.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||79||||4"
msgid "Excuse me, ladies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||80||||4"
msgid "What is it? Is there anything\nwe can assist you with today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||81||||4"
msgid "(If I'm going to rescue Mie-san, I need to\nact like I want into this cult. Let's do this!)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||82||||4"
msgid "Yes. I'm, uh...\nA stray sheep looking for guidance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||83||||4"
msgid "Yes, that much is clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||84||||4"
msgid "Such is the burden of this mortal coil.\nYou are not alone in that feeling."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||85||||4"
msgid "I heard you guys might be able to help me.\nSo, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||86||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Saren Chohabt Atrast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||87||||4"
msgid "Saren Chohabt Atrast?\nThat order is in another town down south."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||88||||4"
msgid "My apologies, but we have nothing to offer you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||89||||4"
msgid "R-Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||90||||4"
msgid "(I really botched that.\nBut how the hell is that a real name...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||91||||4"
msgid "May your journey ahead be blessed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||92||||4"
msgid "(Now what was the name of this cult...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||93||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Aban Chodesht Orest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||94||||4"
msgid "Aban Chodesht Orest?\nThat order is in another town up to the north."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||95||||4"
msgid "My apologies, but we can offer no help to you here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||96||||4"
msgid "R-Right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||97||||4"
msgid "(I really botched that.\nBut seriously? That's a real name?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||98||||4"
msgid "May your journey ahead be blessed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||99||||4"
msgid "(Now what was the name of this cult...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||100||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||101||||4"
msgid "Ah! So the tenets of Munan Chohept Onast run deep\nwithin your veins as well? How wonderful!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||102||||4"
msgid "Glory be!\nYou have arrived in the light!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||103||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it was a long road. I endured a lot\nof hardship, but I'm glad I'm finally here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||104||||4"
msgid "Just relax, you poor thing. Our door\nis always open. Now, come right this way!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||105||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||106||||4"
msgid "Sorry to interrupt you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||107||||4"
msgid "What is it?\nDo you have further business with us?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||108||||4"
msgid "My search for salvation has gone astray.\nI was knocking on all the wrong doors."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||109||||4"
msgid "Which means what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||110||||4"
msgid "Well, I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||111||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Mosan Chohip Istes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||112||||4"
msgid "That's not the same name you said earlier, you know.\nEither way, you clearly lack devotion to our order."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||113||||4"
msgid "It seems I cannot help you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||114||||4"
msgid "Wait, hold on a sec. I'm just tripping over my words a bit.\nI remember now. I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||115||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Miran Choakht Onest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||116||||4"
msgid "I want to join the Order of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||117||||4"
msgid "I see. So you truly seek to become\na disciple of Munan Chohept Onast?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||118||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I think I've finally seen the light."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||119||||4"
msgid "What wonderful news! Very well then!\nPlease, come right this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||120||||4"
msgid "(That went smoother than expected.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||121||||4"
msgid "Come. Right this way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||122||||4"
msgid "There just so happens to have been another lost\nFriend who arrived on our doorstep today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||123||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||124||||4"
msgid "It's nice to meet you, Brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||125||||4"
msgid "(The old man...\nI guess he didn't have any trouble getting in.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||126||||4"
msgid "This gentleman listened quite ardently to my explanation\nof our tenets. He is truly an ideal member already."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||127||||4"
msgid "Right, Brother Suzuki-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||128||||4"
msgid "I'm not worthy of such praise yet, Sister.\nBut hept-onast for the compliment."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||129||||4"
msgid "Hm? What was that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||130||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||131||||4"
msgid "Um, it sounded like you\njust said \"hept-onast.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||132||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast is one of our order's holy words.\nIt is similar in meaning to the phrase \"thank you.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||133||||4"
msgid "R-Right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||134||||4"
msgid "Come, now. She just taught you something.\nShow a little gratitude."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||135||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast very much, Sister."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||136||||4"
msgid "I can show our new Friend\nhere around if you'd like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||137||||4"
msgid "It must be a sign that we turned to the\nlight of Munan Chohept Onast on the same day."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||138||||4"
msgid "What a blessed idea.\nPlease do so."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||139||||4"
msgid "I will be in the other room joining\nour new Friends in the art of shooreh pippi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||140||||4"
msgid "Shooreh pippi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||141||||4"
msgid "Another one of their words, Kiryu-san.\nIt basically means training."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||142||||4"
msgid "So they're training over in that other room?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||143||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I'm sure Mie-san will be with them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||144||||4"
msgid "What the?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||145||||4"
msgid "So this... is shooreh pippi?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||146||||4"
msgid "Yes. It allows them to focus their spirits\nand accumulate kulipaas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||147||||4"
msgid "Kulipaas?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||148||||4"
msgid "In layman's terms, it can be considered a measure\nof virtue. Accumulating kulipaas is vital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||149||||4"
msgid "Only by doing so can a Friend grow closer\nto the divine being Munan Chohept."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||150||||4"
msgid "Uh-huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||151||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast for the explanation, Brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||152||||4"
msgid "You're such a quick learner, Brother Suzuki-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||153||||4"
msgid "Are you sure today is your first Munan Chohept Onast\nexperience? It's astounding to believe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||154||||4"
msgid "You may not even need\nto undergo chomo gomes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||155||||4"
msgid "What's chomo gomes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||156||||4"
msgid "Isn't it obvious, Kiryu-san?\nIt's a word that essentially means brainwashing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||157||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||158||||4"
msgid "They insist it's simply re-education,\nbut there's no doubt what it really is."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||159||||4"
msgid "Do you know what happens when a disciple\nin the Order of Munan Chohept shows signs of doubt?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||160||||4"
msgid "They lock them away and force them\nto undergo chomo gomes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||161||||4"
msgid "This cult is even crazier than I thought.\nThey're insane."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||162||||4"
msgid "You're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||163||||4"
msgid "But he's right, you haven't had any\nproblems blending right in here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||164||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||165||||4"
msgid "You know all their lingo like the back of your hand.\nFor a new \"friend,\" you're pretty familiar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||166||||4"
msgid "...Almost <font_kind=yakuza_italic>too</font_kind> familiar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||167||||4"
msgid "Oh, well, uh... That shows how desperate I am\nto save Mie-san. I must become one of them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||168||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||169||||4"
msgid "Anyway, we should join in\non the shooreh pippi as well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||170||||4"
msgid "Wait, what?\nWe have to do it, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||171||||4"
msgid "We'll stick out like a sore thumb if we don't.\nCome on, hurry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||172||||4"
msgid "Dammit. This is ridiculous..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||173||||4"
msgid "So, old man.\nHave you found Mie-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||174||||4"
msgid "No, not yet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||175||||4"
msgid "She said she was planning on making a huge donation\nto the guru. She's probably purifying in preparation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||176||||4"
msgid "Do we know if she's even in this building...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||177||||4"
msgid "I'm not entirely sure where she is,\nbut we should keep pretending for now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||178||||4"
msgid "No matter what, we need to stop her\nfrom giving them that donation!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||179||||4"
msgid "Ahem! My disciples, please give me your attention!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||180||||4"
msgid "To reward you for undying devotion to shooreh pippi,\nthe guru has decided to grace us with his presence."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||181||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||182||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||183||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||184||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||185||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||186||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||187||||4"
msgid "Our spiritual leader, Munan Akamatsu, has arrived!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||188||||4"
msgid "The guru...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||189||||4"
msgid "The guru...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||190||||4"
msgid "The guru...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||191||||4"
msgid "This clown is their guru?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||192||||4"
msgid "That title has been passed down through the years.\nApparently Akamatsu only took the helm recently."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||193||||4"
msgid "My disciples..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||194||||4"
msgid "Munancho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||195||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||196||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||197||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||198||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||199||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||200||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, say it back!\nThat's how they greet each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||201||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||202||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||203||||4"
msgid "Very nicely done.\nTwo spirit points for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||204||||4"
msgid "(Am I getting graded now?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||205||||4"
msgid "Munancho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||206||||4"
msgid "Minus one spirit point."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||207||||4"
msgid "(Am I getting graded now?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||208||||4"
msgid "(This is absurd.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||209||||4"
msgid "Minus three spirit points."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||210||||4"
msgid "(Am I getting graded now?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||211||||4"
msgid "Good! Glory be. Our divine savior\nMunan Chohept is most pleased."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||212||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||213||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||214||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||215||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||216||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||217||||4"
msgid "Oooh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||218||||4"
msgid "As you are all well aware, the best way to amplify\nthe power of your shooreh pippi is through titherance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||219||||4"
msgid "Only then can you accumulate maximum kulipaas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||220||||4"
msgid "Take our new friend Sister Mie-san for example.\nShe will be offering 100 rinchos today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||221||||4"
msgid "Huh? 100 rinchos!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||222||||4"
msgid "Mie-san sets an example for you all, my disciples."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||223||||4"
msgid "Mie-san is truly a blessed Friend!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||224||||4"
msgid "What immense faith! Your Holiness,\nI too will offer up 100 rinchos of my own tomorrow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||225||||4"
msgid "What are they going on about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||226||||4"
msgid "Rincho is what they call a donation.\nOne is equivalent to... 100,000 yen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||227||||4"
msgid "You mean... Mie-san is going to\ngive this crazy cult 10 million yen?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||228||||4"
msgid "There's no way she has that kind of money."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||229||||4"
msgid "She must have borrowed it from her family.\nWe can't let her go through with this!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||230||||4"
msgid "Now then, my disciples.\nYou may return to the splendor of your shooreh pippi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||231||||4"
msgid "What now, old man? Do you think we'd find\nMie-san if we followed their guru?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||232||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||233||||4"
msgid "Well then, let's do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||234||||4"
msgid "Where are you going, Brothers?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||235||||4"
msgid "Oh, um... We only just joined the order today.\nWe wanted to introduce ourselves to the guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||236||||4"
msgid "Hm... Do you have the rincho necessary to do so?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||238||||4"
msgid "Well, that's actually what I wanted to ask him about."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||239||||4"
msgid "How do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||240||||4"
msgid "I'm but a poor, frail old man. As such, I was planning\non finding a moneylender for my titherance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||241||||4"
msgid "But is a rincho of borrowed money truly acceptable?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||242||||4"
msgid "Would the divine savior Munan Chohept Onast\nstill welcome such a feeble attempt at devotion?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||243||||4"
msgid "Of course he would."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||244||||4"
msgid "Your devout nature is deeply moving, Brother.\nYou have no need to doubt yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||245||||4"
msgid "Ah, I'm so glad to hear that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||246||||4"
msgid "But honestly, I'm still afraid to go to a moneylender.\nSome direct encouragement from the guru could help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||247||||4"
msgid "(The old man lies through his\nteeth like it's nothing...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||248||||4"
msgid "Very well, I will show you to him.\nYou have adequately proven your devotion. However..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||249||||4"
msgid "What about you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||250||||4"
msgid "Are you a sincere follower of Munan Chohept Onast?\nMind if I ask you a few questions to confirm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||251||||4"
msgid "A test?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||252||||4"
msgid "I must be sure you will not embarrass\nyourself in front of the guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||253||||4"
msgid "Worry not. If you have listened attentively,\nit should be a simple task for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||254||||4"
msgid "Fine. I'll ace this, no problem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||255||||4"
msgid "Very well.\nQuestion one will test your basic understanding."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||256||||4"
msgid "In the Order of Munan Chohept Onast,\nhow does one express gratitude?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||257||||4"
msgid "Dolche uho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||258||||4"
msgid "Did you say dolche uho...?\nHow dare you utter those words!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||259||||4"
msgid "That phrase is reserved only for our guru!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||260||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kiryu-san! You can't say that!\nDolche uho means, um..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||261||||4"
msgid "It means \"drink my breast milk\"!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||262||||4"
msgid "...Why would the guru ever say that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||263||||4"
msgid "The correct answer is hept-onast.\nPlease remember that going forward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||264||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast for telling me, Brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||265||||4"
msgid "Munancho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||266||||4"
msgid "Incorrect. That is our greeting, remember?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||267||||4"
msgid "The correct answer is hept-onast.\nPlease remember that going forward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||268||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast for telling me, Brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||269||||4"
msgid "Hept-onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||270||||4"
msgid "Glory be! That's correct!\nIt seems you were paying close attention."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||271||||4"
msgid "That one was easy.\nI could pass this test in my sleep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||272||||4"
msgid "Now then, on to question two."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||273||||4"
msgid "Through shooreh pippi, you accumulate a particular\nunit of virtue. What does our order call that unit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||274||||4"
msgid "Kulipaas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||275||||4"
msgid "Almost! The correct answer is kulipaas.\nMost new disciples struggle with that question."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||276||||4"
msgid "Damn, I should be better than that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||277||||4"
msgid "Kulipaas."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||278||||4"
msgid "Correct! Glory be, it seems you have studied well.\nYou are quite a promising disciple."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||279||||4"
msgid "Yes. It's all thanks to my devoted shooreh pippi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||280||||4"
msgid "Kulibaaf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||281||||4"
msgid "Almost! The correct answer is kulipaas.\nMost new disciples struggle with that question."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||282||||4"
msgid "Damn, I should be better than that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||283||||4"
msgid "Moving right along. Question three."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||284||||4"
msgid "Please tell me the full name of the guru\nof the Order of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||285||||4"
msgid "Munan Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||286||||4"
msgid "Ah, so very close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||287||||4"
msgid "Munan Suzuki is actually our order's founder.\nI'm surprised you've heard about him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||288||||4"
msgid "Wait, really? I was just guessing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||289||||4"
msgid "Years ago, Munan Suzuki was arrested due to\nthe government's irrational fear of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||290||||4"
msgid "They falsely accused our order\nof being a scam, and our guru a fraud."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||291||||4"
msgid "However, under Munan Akamatsu's holy guidance,\nour order will endure eternally. Glory be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||293||||4"
msgid "Munan Akamatsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||294||||4"
msgid "Wonderfully done.\nThat may have been a bit too simple, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||295||||4"
msgid "I'd never mistake the name of our holy guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||296||||4"
msgid "Munan Akamatsu inherited his power\nfrom our order's founder, Munan Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||297||||4"
msgid "Munan Suzuki...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||298||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, Munan Suzuki was arrested due to\nthe government's irrational fear of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||299||||4"
msgid "They falsely accused our order\nof being a scam, and our guru a fraud."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||300||||4"
msgid "However, under Munan Akamatsu's holy guidance,\nour order will endure eternally. Glory be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||302||||4"
msgid "Munan Sato."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||303||||4"
msgid "What? How have you mistaken the name of our guru!?\nThe correct answer is Munan Akamatsu. Such impiety."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||304||||4"
msgid "Oh, I remember now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||305||||4"
msgid "Please commit this to memory. Munan Akamatsu inherited\nhis power from our order's founder, Munan Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||306||||4"
msgid "Munan Suzuki...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||307||||4"
msgid "Unfortunately, Munan Suzuki was arrested due to\nthe government's irrational fear of Munan Chohept Onast."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||308||||4"
msgid "They falsely accused our order\nof being a scam, and our guru a fraud."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||309||||4"
msgid "However, under Munan Akamatsu's holy guidance,\nour order will endure eternally. Glory be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||311||||4"
msgid "At last, the final question is upon us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||312||||4"
msgid "Please describe the true meaning of chomo gomes.\nDo you know the answer?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||313||||4"
msgid "It's brainwashing, isn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||314||||4"
msgid "Excuse me? Brainwashing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||315||||4"
msgid "There is no such word within our holy order.\nWho told you such blasphemy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||318||||4"
msgid "It seems I cannot allow you to meet the guru. Your test\nhas concluded. Please return to your shooreh pippi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||319||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I really need to see him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||320||||4"
msgid "You must earn an audience with our guru, Brother.\nYour understanding is greatly appreciated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||321||||4"
msgid "If you still insist..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||322||||4"
msgid "What'll happen?\nAre you going to chomo gomes me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||323||||4"
msgid "Precisely. It is the only course of action available."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||324||||4"
msgid "Try me. I'm not afraid of this chomo gomes crap."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||325||||4"
msgid "Guards!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||326||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||327||||4"
msgid "Now, show this impudent disciple what\nhappens when you defy Munan Chohept Onast!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||328||||4"
msgid "Munancho!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||329||||4"
msgid "Re-education."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||330||||4"
msgid "Precisely. I am afraid that was too easy for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||332||||4"
msgid "Sex education."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||333||||4"
msgid "You mean re-education!\nThat's an odd mistake to make... Was that intentional?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||334||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||335||||4"
msgid "That concludes our test."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||336||||4"
msgid "I must say, incredible job."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||337||||4"
msgid "This is but your first day in our order, but you clearly\nhold Munan Chohept Onast dear to your heart."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||338||||4"
msgid "That was amazing, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||339||||4"
msgid "I hope our other new Friends will follow in\nyour footsteps. You have passed the test."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||340||||4"
msgid "Oh, it was nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||341||||4"
msgid "As the two of you requested, I will introduce\nyou to our holy guru. Please follow me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||342||||4"
msgid "(Mie-san should be in the back with the guru.\nI hope she hasn't given her titherance yet...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||343||||4"
msgid "It seems you have solid fundamentals.\nContinue the hard work to reach salvation, Brother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||344||||4"
msgid "I will. Before that though,\nwill you let us meet with the guru?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||345||||4"
msgid "Yes. As requested, I will introduce him to you.\nPlease follow me, Brothers."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||346||||4"
msgid "(Mie-san should be in the back with the guru.\nI hope she hasn't given her titherance yet...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||347||||4"
msgid "Hm... It appears you have yet to imbue\nthe values of shooreh pippi into your being."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||348||||4"
msgid "This is but your first day, but you don't seem particularly\ninvested in our order. You cannot meet the guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||349||||4"
msgid "I'd appreciate it if you made an exception,\njust for a few minutes. Please let me see him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||350||||4"
msgid "I cannot."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||351||||4"
msgid "Please, we'll make it quick!\nI'll give a rincho for my friend as well!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||352||||4"
msgid "No means no."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||353||||4"
msgid "But...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||355||||4"
msgid "Please, return to your shooreh pippi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||356||||4"
msgid "Sorry, but I really need to see him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||357||||4"
msgid "You must earn an audience with our guru, Brother.\nYour understanding is greatly appreciated."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||358||||4"
msgid "If you still insist..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||359||||4"
msgid "What'll happen?\nAre you going to chomo gomes me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||360||||4"
msgid "Your eyes betray your true nature, Brother.\nYou are but a demon who lacks the fear of faith..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||361||||4"
msgid "Just take me to your damn guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||362||||4"
msgid "Guards!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||363||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||364||||4"
msgid "Now, show this impudent disciple what\nhappens when you defy Munan Chohept Onast!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||365||||4"
msgid "Hey, are these guys really done already?\nI don't think your chomo gomes worked very well."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||367||||4"
msgid "Y-You're incredible, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||368||||4"
msgid "Why don't you take us to the founder now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||369||||4"
msgid "V-Very well, then.\nPlease come with me, you two."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||370||||4"
msgid "(Mie-san should be in the back with the guru.\nI hope she hasn't given her titherance yet...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||371||||4"
msgid "Excuse me, Your Holiness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||372||||4"
msgid "What is it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||373||||4"
msgid "Our new Friends here have requested\nan audience with you. They only just joined today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||374||||4"
msgid "Both of them are immensely devoted.\nPlease offer them your blessing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||375||||4"
msgid "Their faith is promising, though not fully developed yet.\nPlease offer them your blessing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||376||||4"
msgid "They're, well... They have a few issues. They are quite\npassionate though, so please offer them your blessing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||377||||4"
msgid "Very well, then. It fills my heart with joy to\nsee you here, Friends. Please accept this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||378||||4"
msgid "Some blessing this is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||379||||4"
msgid "Did you say something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||380||||4"
msgid "No..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||381||||4"
msgid "Your Holiness, Mie-san's purification is complete.\nShe is ready for the 100 rincho titherance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||382||||4"
msgid "Very well. This is a crucial ceremony, my new Friends.\nReturn to your shooreh pippi at once."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||383||||4"
msgid "Mie-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||384||||4"
msgid "Huh? Suzuki-san?\nWhat're ya doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||385||||4"
msgid "Please, head back to the other room."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||386||||4"
msgid "Mie-san, you can't go through with this!\nThis order is nothing but a scam!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||387||||4"
msgid "Don't give them a single yen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||388||||4"
msgid "Silence!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||389||||4"
msgid "Suzuki-san! That's enough o' yer blasphemy!\nApologize to the guru, now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||390||||4"
msgid "I won't!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||391||||4"
msgid "It appears you misunderstand our order's intentions.\nI am aware that many perceive us as a simple scam."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||392||||4"
msgid "However, our faith burns bright\nthrough the darkness of their slander."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||393||||4"
msgid "Our love for Munan Chohept Onast\nwill carry us across the ocean of lies around us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||394||||4"
msgid "You are free to doubt our order, but you will face divine\npunishment if you disrupt the faith of an innocent Friend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||395||||4"
msgid "Huh. You've really grown into an expert con artist."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||396||||4"
msgid "Akamatsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||397||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||398||||4"
msgid "Old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||399||||4"
msgid "You used to be Munan Chohept Onast's treasurer, yes?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||400||||4"
msgid "After the arrest of the founder Munan Suzuki,\nyou took over the order with money you had stashed away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||401||||4"
msgid "Just who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||403||||4"
msgid "I know I've aged,\nbut you should still recognize me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||404||||4"
msgid "W-Wait..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||405||||4"
msgid "I used to be known as Munan Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||406||||4"
msgid "You're Munan Suzuki?\nNo way...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||407||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||408||||4"
msgid "What are you doing here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||409||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, Mie-san. I'm sorry for hiding this from you.\nHowever, this is my true identity."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||410||||4"
msgid "The divine savior Munan Chohept Onast doesn't exist.\nI dreamed him up years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||411||||4"
msgid "All of your prayers have fallen on deaf ears."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||412||||4"
msgid "Listen to me, Mie-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||413||||4"
msgid "Your late husband would be turning in his grave\nif he saw you now. You know that, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||415||||4"
msgid "Are you sure you want to go through\nwith this 100 rincho titherance?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||417||||4"
msgid "How ridiculous.\nYou've become quite the joke, Munan Suzuki."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||418||||4"
msgid "And you used to be the gold standard of frauds.\nDid your time in prison soften you up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||419||||4"
msgid "That's not it. I just can't stand\nto see my crimes carried on anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||420||||4"
msgid "You traitor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||421||||4"
msgid "Lock the doors!\nDon't let anyone else in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||422||||4"
msgid "Lock the doors!\nDon't let anyone else in!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||423||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||424||||4"
msgid "What are you going to do, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||425||||4"
msgid "Suzuki-san, Mie-san. Stand back.\nThis might get a little ugly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||426||||4"
msgid "How dare you slander Munan Chohept Onast!\nThe only way forward for you is... chomo gomes!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||427||||4"
msgid "It hurts... It hurts so much..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||428||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||429||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||430||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||431||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||432||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||433||||4"
msgid "What's wrong, Your Holiness?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||434||||4"
msgid "Ah, Friends!\nHurry, you must call me an ambulance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||435||||4"
msgid "Our guru is gravely injured!\nWe must perform the Ritual of Healing, everyone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||436||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||437||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||438||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||439||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||440||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||441||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||442||||4"
msgid "Y-You dipshits!\nThat's not gonna fix a damn thing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||443||||4"
msgid "You know, I'm getting the craziest deja vu...\nI feel like I was in this exact situation before."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||444||||4"
msgid "Stop waving your hands around\nand call me an ambulance!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||446||||4"
msgid "Mie-san should be okay now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||447||||4"
msgid "The other disciples heard what happened.\nThey've been leaving the cult in droves."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||448||||4"
msgid "This is all because of you, Kiryu-san.\nI can't thank you enough."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||449||||4"
msgid "Here. This is a token of my appreciation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||450||||4"
msgid "Can I ask you something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||451||||4"
msgid "You ended up demolishing this order's resurgence,\nbut is that the real reason you came to this town?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||452||||4"
msgid "To be honest... no."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||453||||4"
msgid "I was actually thinking I would reclaim\nmy position as Munan Chohept Onast's guru."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||454||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||455||||4"
msgid "After I got out of jail, I had nowhere to go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||456||||4"
msgid "But if I returned to be the guru,\nI knew I could belong somewhere again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||457||||4"
msgid "I didn't plan on meeting someone as wonderful\nas Mie-san before I got back to the order, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||458||||4"
msgid "And well, I didn't expect\nI'd fall in love with her, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||459||||4"
msgid "What about Mie-san?\nHas she said anything to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||460||||4"
msgid "Not a word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||461||||4"
msgid "I'm not surprised. I spent a long time deceiving\npeople just like her. I destroyed countless lives, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||463||||4"
msgid "It's only right that I pay the price for that now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||464||||4"
msgid "I guess the sins you commit never really fade away..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||465||||4"
msgid "Even so, I feel like what we did today was\nthe first step toward atoning for my past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||466||||4"
msgid "I wouldn't have been able to do it\nwithout you and Mie-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||467||||4"
msgid "If there really is a divine being out there..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||speech_list_sub_b02||table||468||||4"
msgid "...I'm sure he'd be lenient on a guy\nwho faces his sins head on like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||0||||4"
msgid "Fine tofu for sale!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||1||||4"
msgid "Hey, you there!\nHow about some tofu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||2||||4"
msgid "Hm? No thanks, I'm good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||3||||4"
msgid "You just don't know how tasty it is!\nPlease! Won't you give it a shot?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||4||||4"
msgid "I told you I don't want any."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||5||||4"
msgid "You'd only have to buy one!\nIf you don't, I won't..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||6||||4"
msgid "You're annoying me now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||7||||4"
msgid "Hm...? Wait..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||8||||4"
msgid "No way... Pocket Circuit Fighter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||9||||4"
msgid "Huh? Wait...\nAren't you... Kazuma-kun!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||10||||4"
msgid "It's been too long...\nWe met way back in the bubble, so..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||11||||4"
msgid "I guess it's been about 30 years."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||12||||4"
msgid "Has it been that long?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||13||||4"
msgid "It feels like only yesterday that we were\nracing Pocket Circuit cars in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||14||||4"
msgid "Yeah. It's weird, but I feel the same way.\nThose were the days..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||15||||4"
msgid "But man, you've really aged.\nI didn't even recognize you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||16||||4"
msgid "Heh, likewise. You don't yell with\nquite the same gusto you had then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||17||||4"
msgid "Hmm, really?\nWell, people change."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||18||||4"
msgid "Never figured I'd run into you in Onomichi...\nYou're running a tofu shop?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||19||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Not long after I retired,\nI came back to Hiroshima, my hometown."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||20||||4"
msgid "What about you?\nHere to see the sights?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||21||||4"
msgid "Nah, I'm here on business,\nso I'll be around for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||22||||4"
msgid "I see. Then, if our schedules line up,\nwe should catch up over some<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||23||||4"
msgid "[Hey! Daddy!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||24||||4"
msgid "Hm? \"Daddy\"?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||25||||4"
msgid "Let me introduce you.\nThis is Sakito, my son!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||26||||4"
msgid "Pocket Circuit Fighter has a son!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||27||||4"
msgid "Heh... So you finally became a man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||28||||4"
msgid "Let's not dwell on that, maybe..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||29||||4"
msgid "[Daddy!] Who is this guy?\n[Who is this dandy man?]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||30||||4"
msgid "This guy was one of my racing buddies.\nHis name's Kazuma-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||31||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-san? How do you do?\n[Nice to meet you!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||32||||4"
msgid "[N-Nice to...]\nSome kid you've got there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||33||||4"
msgid "Surprised? We decided he should\nhave daily English lessons."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||34||||4"
msgid "English lessons...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||35||||4"
msgid "Hm? Wait, Sakito.\nDon't you have English class today?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||36||||4"
msgid "Um, well..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||37||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||38||||4"
msgid "There you are!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||39||||4"
msgid "[M-Mommy...]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||40||||4"
msgid "You better hurry, or you'll be late for\nEnglish class! Don't make this hard for Mommy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||41||||4"
msgid "[But...] But..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||42||||4"
msgid "Don't talk back! Listen, Sakito.\nSociety is only going to go more global!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||43||||4"
msgid "If you can't speak English, you'll end up\nrunning a tacky tofu shop like your daddy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||44||||4"
msgid "..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||45||||4"
msgid "[Sorry Mommy...]\nI'll go to my English class now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||46||||4"
msgid "As long as you understand.\nNow let's get going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||47||||4"
msgid "As for you! How long are you going to\nbe a bad influence on Sakito!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||48||||4"
msgid "If you have time to lollygag, then you\nhave time to sell tofu for his college fund!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||49||||4"
msgid "Y-Yes, absolutely..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||50||||4"
msgid "Sorry, Kazuma-kun. You shouldn't\nhave had to see such a pathetic display..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||51||||4"
msgid "It's fine. That was your wife?\nShe's pretty intense..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||52||||4"
msgid "Haha... Yeeaah...\nBut she's good in her own way."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||53||||4"
msgid "She'll do whatever it takes to make\nsure Sakito grows up good and strong."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||54||||4"
msgid "We can't let him take after me, after all..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||55||||4"
msgid "I can't say I agree with that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||56||||4"
msgid "Well, anyway, I need to get back to work.\nKazuma-kun, it was great seeing you again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||57||||4"
msgid "If you're still in the area later,\nstop by again so we can catch up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||58||||4"
msgid "Sure thing.\nGood luck with the tofu, Pocket Circuit Fighter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||59||||4"
msgid "Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||60||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kazuma-kun.\nHow about some tofu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||61||||4"
msgid "Thanks a lot.\nCome back again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||62||||4"
msgid "Come back again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||63||||4"
msgid "Oh. Kazuma-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||64||||4"
msgid "Hm? You're Pocket Circuit Fighter's son."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||65||||4"
msgid "Sakito.\n[My name is Sakito.]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||66||||4"
msgid "Sorry, that's right.\nWhat are you doing here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||67||||4"
msgid "There's still some time before my English\nclass starts, so I was just spacing out."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||68||||4"
msgid "Is that so?\nBy the way, how old are you, Sakito?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||69||||4"
msgid "[Eight years old!]"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||70||||4"
msgid "[Eight...] That means \"eight\" right?\nYou speak English really well for your age."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||71||||4"
msgid "It's nothing special, really.\nI don't really care about learning English..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||72||||4"
msgid "You don't?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||73||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I have to go to English class every day.\nI'm sick of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||74||||4"
msgid "Mr. Kazuma-san,\nwhat were you like at my age?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||75||||4"
msgid "Hmm. Well, I certainly didn't study as much as you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||76||||4"
msgid "Oh really?\n...That'd be nice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||77||||4"
msgid "Yeah. I used to hang out with your dad a lot.\nAlthough I was already a grown man by then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||78||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah, you're friends with Daddy, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||79||||4"
msgid "Yeah, sure am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||80||||4"
msgid "We raced Pocket Circuit cars together back then.\nEveryone called him Pocket Circuit Fighter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||81||||4"
msgid "Pocket Circuit... Fighter?\nWhat did Daddy do back then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||82||||4"
msgid "Hm? Your dad never told\nyou about Pocket Circuit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||83||||4"
msgid "Well... I'm not supposed to talk\nto Daddy unless I have to..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||84||||4"
msgid "You're not allowed?\nWhy's that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||85||||4"
msgid "Mommy says if I talk to Daddy,\nhe'll be \"a bad inflooenz.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||86||||4"
msgid "He must mean the Fighter's wife..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||87||||4"
msgid "She was pretty rough on Fighter\nwhen I saw them earlier..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||88||||4"
msgid "Do your mom and dad\nnot get along well?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||89||||4"
msgid "I don't know. Daddy says it wasn't\nlike this back in Tokyo..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||90||||4"
msgid "He says when they came back here,\nMommy turned to the dark side."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||91||||4"
msgid "But she doesn't like it when I talk to\nDaddy, especially about his past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||92||||4"
msgid "I get it now... And you just want to be\ncloser to your dad, is that right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||93||||4"
msgid "Yeah... I want to ask Daddy\nabout a lot of stuff..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||94||||4"
msgid "We share a house and stuff...\nBut I don't even know my daddy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||95||||4"
msgid "Is that even a real family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||96||||4"
msgid "I understand, I get that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||97||||4"
msgid "If he won't tell you though,\nthen I'll tell you about your dad!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||98||||4"
msgid "Huh? Really? You will?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||99||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Pocket Circuit bound us together.\nAsk me anything you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||100||||4"
msgid "Yay! [Thank you,] Mr. Kazuma-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||101||||4"
msgid "But, what exactly <font_kind=yakuza_italic>is</font_kind> Pocket Circuit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||102||||4"
msgid "Right, I should explain that first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||103||||4"
msgid "Pocket Circuit is... Well, you have a little car,\nand then there are all these parts..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||104||||4"
msgid "You know what, it might be easier to just\nshow you rather than trying to explain it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||105||||4"
msgid "But... Where could I find a Pocket Circuit\ncar in this day and age?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||106||||4"
msgid "Oh, I know! Sakito, have you ever seen\nany small toy cars at your house?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||107||||4"
msgid "Toy cars? Hmm, I don't think so..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||108||||4"
msgid "Oh! I think I saw a small box with\na picture of a car on it in the closet."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||109||||4"
msgid "That's probably a Pocket Circuit kit!\nSakito, could you bring it to me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||110||||4"
msgid "Yeah, no problem! I'll be right back!\nLet's meet up here in a little bit, okay!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||111||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Just make sure your mom's not watching."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||112||||4"
msgid "Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||113||||4"
msgid "Oh, Mr. Kazuma-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||114||||4"
msgid "Hey, Sakito.\nDid you find it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||115||||4"
msgid "Is this it?\nIs this a Pocket Circuit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||116||||4"
msgid "Yep, that's a Pocket Circuit machine!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||117||||4"
msgid "So this is Pocket Circuit..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||118||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Your dad and I were really into these\nwhen we were young. This takes me back..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||119||||4"
msgid "Daddy played with this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||120||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-san. Will this car still work?\nI wanna try playing Pocket Circuit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||121||||4"
msgid "Maybe it would...!\nSure! Wanna put it together?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||122||||4"
msgid "Yeah!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||123||||4"
msgid "There, done."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||124||||4"
msgid "Wow! That's so cool!\nI wanna drive it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||125||||4"
msgid "Sakito! What are you doing here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||126||||4"
msgid "Oh, Daddy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||127||||4"
msgid "Hey, Fighter.\nYou came at a great time!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||128||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-kun? What's going on?\nD-Don't tell me that's..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||129||||4"
msgid "Look, look!\nI built it with Mr. Kazuma-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||130||||4"
msgid "Isn't it cool!?\nNow we can play Pocket Circuit...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||131||||4"
msgid "Stop this tomfoolery! At once!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||132||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||133||||4"
msgid "It's almost time for your English class!\nYour mother will blow a fuse if you skip class!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||134||||4"
msgid "And how dare you rifle through my closet!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||135||||4"
msgid "If you have time to play with toys,\nyou have time to study your English!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||136||||4"
msgid "Hey, Fighter...\nThis is on me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||137||||4"
msgid "D... Da...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||138||||4"
msgid "D-Daddy, you suck!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||139||||4"
msgid "Hey, Sakito!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||140||||4"
msgid "Fighter, I'm the one who told Sakito\nto get a Pocket Circuit kit from your house."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||141||||4"
msgid "I apologize for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||142||||4"
msgid "But... You didn't have to lay\ninto him like that, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||143||||4"
msgid "I hear you, but if he skips English class,\nhe'll get an earful from his mother."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||144||||4"
msgid "This is best for Sakito. I like you Kazuma-kun, but you\nshould stay away if you're going to jeopardize his future."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||145||||4"
msgid "Fighter... You've changed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||146||||4"
msgid "Changed... Maybe I have.\nBut I don't exactly have a choice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||147||||4"
msgid "If Sakito is going to lead a good life\nafter being born to a loser like me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||148||||4"
msgid "...He has to work twice as\nhard as everyone else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||149||||4"
msgid "So... Me and Sakito need to make\nmy wife's plan our first priority."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||150||||4"
msgid "Your son just wants to know more\nabout you, his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||151||||4"
msgid "Huh...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||152||||4"
msgid "He asked me about you when you were younger.\nDid you know he doesn't feel he can talk to you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||153||||4"
msgid "He just wants to know who you are...\nAnd you shouldn't keep that from him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||154||||4"
msgid "B-But... I might be a bad influence on him,\nand I'd get in the way of his studies..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||155||||4"
msgid "Fighter. Back in the day, you made so many\nkids happy through Pocket Circuit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||157||||4"
msgid "Yes, you were irresponsible, insecure, and clumsy...\nBut the kids all trusted you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||158||||4"
msgid "That's because, back then,\nyou could see things from their point of view."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||160||||4"
msgid "If you could do it back then, you should\nhave no problem making your only son smile."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||161||||4"
msgid "Am I wrong, Pocket Circuit Fighter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||162||||4"
msgid "K-Kazuma-kun..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||163||||4"
msgid "I'm just a different person now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||164||||4"
msgid "Back then, I loved being the fighter,\nbut it was my job to play that role..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||165||||4"
msgid "So the best I can do for him now is\nwatch over him from a distance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||166||||4"
msgid "We're done here.\nYou disappoint me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||167||||4"
msgid "I'm worried about Sakito.\nI'm gonna go look for him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||168||||4"
msgid "He'll probably go where\nhe can see the ocean."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||169||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||170||||4"
msgid "Whenever he's down, he goes to\nlook at the ocean and mope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||171||||4"
msgid "I see. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||172||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-kun. I'm really sorry\nthat it's you making this right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||174||||4"
msgid "Sakito's somewhere near the ocean, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||175||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Whenever he's down,\nhe goes to look at the ocean and mope."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||176||||4"
msgid "I see. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||177||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-kun. I'm really sorry.\nPlease make things right..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||179||||4"
msgid "Ow, that stings!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||180||||4"
msgid "Li'l brat!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||181||||4"
msgid "I-I'm sorry..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||182||||4"
msgid "Hm? Isn't that Sakito?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||183||||4"
msgid "Whaddaya think yer doin', running\nyer toys into people's feet? Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||184||||4"
msgid "I-I'm sorry...\nI lost control of it for a sec..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||185||||4"
msgid "If apologies fixed everythin',\nwe wouldn't have the cops!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||186||||4"
msgid "Yer gonna have t'show\nus where y'live, kid!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||187||||4"
msgid "I'd say yer parents owe some\ncash to cover a doctor's visit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||188||||4"
msgid "C-Come on...\nIt was just a little bump..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||189||||4"
msgid "The fuck y'say, brat!?\nGet your parents, now! Or else..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||190||||4"
msgid "S-Stop it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||191||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||192||||4"
msgid "That car is part of my daddy's past!\nPlease! Please just stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||193||||4"
msgid "I just want my daddy to be happy again!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||194||||4"
msgid "Huh? T'hell you sayin?\nY'got some nerve, kid!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||195||||4"
msgid "These punks...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||196||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-kun. Leave this to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||197||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||198||||4"
msgid "Hey! Back away from that kid!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||199||||4"
msgid "The... hell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||200||||4"
msgid "Who are you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||201||||4"
msgid "I am... Pocket Circuit Fighter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||202||||4"
msgid "P-Pocket Circuit Fighter?\nThe fuck...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||203||||4"
msgid "D-Daddy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||204||||4"
msgid "Hm? So you're this brat's daddy!\nY'saved us the trouble of findin' ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||205||||4"
msgid "No... I have no right to\ncall myself his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||206||||4"
msgid "It's only because I pushed him\naway that he's in danger now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||207||||4"
msgid "I'm so pathetic..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||208||||4"
msgid "What're ya mumblin' about!? Just give\nus the cash before we beat it outta ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||209||||4"
msgid "I don't have a single yen for\nvillains who make children cry!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||210||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||211||||4"
msgid "Sakito... I lost my confidence.\nThat's why I kept running from you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||212||||4"
msgid "I couldn't bear the thought...\nthat you might end up like me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||213||||4"
msgid "Daddy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||214||||4"
msgid "But... I won't run anymore!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||215||||4"
msgid "Your dad might be a weak, awkward loser,\nbut he's gonna give it his all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||216||||4"
msgid "So... Never forget this moment, Sakito!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||217||||4"
msgid "...Okay!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||218||||4"
msgid "Daddy... No, Father!\nYou can beat these guys!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||219||||4"
msgid "Apparently you both wanna die?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||220||||4"
msgid "Aniki! Looks like our back-up\ngot here just in time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||221||||4"
msgid "Uh, whoa whoa whoa...\nI-Isn't five-on-one kinda unfair..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||222||||4"
msgid "Gonna piss your pants?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||223||||4"
msgid "If you've got your back-up,\nit's only fair if I back up Fighter, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||224||||4"
msgid "K-Kazuma-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||225||||4"
msgid "Eh? What's your deal?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||226||||4"
msgid "I'm a friend of Fighter's. And anyone who\npicks on kids... is on my shit list."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||227||||4"
msgid "So you wanna share a grave or somethin'?\nCouple'a dumbfucks here, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||228||||4"
msgid "Fine, y'assholes! Y'can die together,\nbeing that you're best buds and all!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||229||||4"
msgid "What's up with this guy!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||230||||4"
msgid "A-Aniki! Let's beat it!\nThey're gonna murder us!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||231||||4"
msgid "Kazuma-kun... Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||232||||4"
msgid "I really am a pathetic father.\nI'm all bark and no bite..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||233||||4"
msgid "If you hadn't showed up, I'd have gotten\ntoo beat up to even protect Sakito..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||234||||4"
msgid "Fighter... I wouldn't say you're pathetic."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||235||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||236||||4"
msgid "Father! Are you okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||237||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'm fine.\nAre you okay, Sakito?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||238||||4"
msgid "Yeah! Mr. Kazuma-san and\nPocket Circuit Fighter protected me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||239||||4"
msgid "You're so cool as Pocket Circuit Fighter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||240||||4"
msgid "I wanna know who Pocket Circuit Fighter really is...\nWho my father is!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||241||||4"
msgid "Sakito..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||242||||4"
msgid "Sakito! There you are! \nWhat exactly is going on here!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||243||||4"
msgid "Oh, Mommy..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||244||||4"
msgid "And why are you dressed in\nthat stupid old get-up!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||245||||4"
msgid "You endangered Sakito with\nyour stupid antics, didn't you!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||246||||4"
msgid "I-I..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||247||||4"
msgid "That's wrong, Mommy.\nPocket Circuit Fighter protec<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||248||||4"
msgid "I've heard enough excuses!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||249||||4"
msgid "We don't have time to discuss this!\nYou're already late for English class!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||250||||4"
msgid "What in the world were you all thinking!?\nAre you trying to make my life miserable!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||251||||4"
msgid "Mommy... I...\nI don't want to go to English class today!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||252||||4"
msgid "Nonsense! What would you propose is a\nbetter use of time than learning English!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||253||||4"
msgid "I wanna play with my father..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||255||||4"
msgid "Absolutely not! Sakito, don't you care about\nyour future? And it's \"daddy\", not \"father!\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||256||||4"
msgid "Look at your daddy!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||257||||4"
msgid "He had no choice but to inherit a tofu shop\nbecause he goofed off until he was 50!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||258||||4"
msgid "He's a sad, meek, tofu-hawking loser\nwho can't even stand up to his own wife!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||259||||4"
msgid "Is that how you want to end up!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||261||||4"
msgid "I don't even know whether or\nnot I want to be like Daddy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||262||||4"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||263||||4"
msgid "I don't know the first thing about him.\nHow could I know if I want to be like him?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||264||||4"
msgid "That's why I want to get to know him.\nI wanna be friends with my Daddy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||265||||4"
msgid "And once I know him...\nThen I can figure out the future!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||266||||4"
msgid "Sakito! Hold on!\nWould you say something to your son!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||267||||4"
msgid "Sakito... I'm sorry you just had to say all that.\nI've really failed you as a father all this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||268||||4"
msgid "Father..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||269||||4"
msgid "But, I'm gonna be a real dad now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||270||||4"
msgid "I want to raise you with confidence,\nlike a real father should."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||271||||4"
msgid "Misaki. Call the English school and tell them\nhe'll be spending the day with his father."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||272||||4"
msgid "Now just one minute!\nI refuse to allow such<symbol=em_dash_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||273||||4"
msgid "BE QUIET!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||275||||4"
msgid "Sure, I may have been forced into the family\nbusiness, and yeah, I suck at making tofu!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||276||||4"
msgid "And, I'm totally whipped by my wife!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||277||||4"
msgid "But! I am his father!\nHe wants to spend time with me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||278||||4"
msgid "If you want me to ignore my son's feelings,\nthen... You may as well kill me now!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||279||||4"
msgid "H-Honey..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||280||||4"
msgid "Father..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||281||||4"
msgid "Please, Misaki.\nLet me be a father to our son."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||283||||4"
msgid "Fine. You have my permission."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||284||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||285||||4"
msgid "Huh? I-It's really okay?\nEven skipping English...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||286||||4"
msgid "Yes. But when you come home, you're\ncatching up on your lessons. Understood?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||287||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah! I will!\nI promise!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||288||||4"
msgid "I need to relax, don't I? I've just been so\nstressed about Sakito's future lately..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||289||||4"
msgid "And..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||290||||4"
msgid "And...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||291||||4"
msgid "I don't know what just got into you,\nbut that was the man I fell in love with."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||292||||4"
msgid "Misaki..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||293||||4"
msgid "Well, I'll go call the school."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||294||||4"
msgid "Mom... Thank you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||295||||4"
msgid "Sakito. Your dad was pretty cool, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||296||||4"
msgid "Yeah! Super cool!\nI didn't know he could yell so loud!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||297||||4"
msgid "You're embarrassing me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||298||||4"
msgid "Sakito, I'm sorry I wasn't paying\nattention to your feelings!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||299||||4"
msgid "No, it's okay!\nYou were there for me when it counted!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||300||||4"
msgid "Sakito... All right!\nIt's time for a Pocket Circuit battle!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||301||||4"
msgid "Yeah! I wanna try Pocket Circuit!\nYou were really fast, right, Dad?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||302||||4"
msgid "Is there any doubt!?\nI'm the one and only... Pocket Circuit Fighter!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||304||||4"
msgid "Okay! Let's have a race to see who\ncan get the cars from my closet first!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||305||||4"
msgid "Ready, go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||307||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kazuma-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||308||||4"
msgid "Hey. How've things with your son\nbeen since I saw you last?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||309||||4"
msgid "They're going well, thanks to you.\nHe's been getting really into Pocket Circuit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||310||||4"
msgid "That's great. Guess the need\nfor speed runs in the family."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||311||||4"
msgid "Oh, by the way. I heard you're putting\na crew together. Is the rumor true?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||312||||4"
msgid "Oh, by the way. I heard you're putting\na crew together. Is the rumor true?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||313||||4"
msgid "Oh, by the way. I heard you're putting\na crew together. Is the rumor true?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||314||||4"
msgid "Hm? Yeah, I am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||315||||4"
msgid "If you've got room for one more...\nHow about I join you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||316||||4"
msgid "If you've got room for one more...\nHow about I join you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||317||||4"
msgid "Huh? You? I appreciate it, but this\ngroup is pretty dangerous actually..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||318||||4"
msgid "I was just thinking back to that fight,\nand as a father, I want to be stronger."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||319||||4"
msgid "So, if I go with you,\nI know I can get there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||320||||4"
msgid "So, if I go with you,\nI know I can get there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||321||||4"
msgid "Besides, it's only natural to help\nout your friend when they need it!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||322||||4"
msgid "All right then.\nI'll be expecting great things."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||323||||4"
msgid "Leave it to me!\nLet's do it, Kazuma-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||324||||4"
msgid "Hey, Kazuma-kun.\nWant some tofu!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||325||||4"
msgid "Thanks a lot!\nCome back soon, okay!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||speech_list_sub_b03||table||326||||4"
msgid "Come back soon, Kazuma-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||0||||4"
msgid "Hm? It feels like someone's watching me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||1||||4"
msgid "I must be imagining it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||3||||4"
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||4||||4"
msgid "No time for questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||6||||4"
msgid "What the hell just happened to me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||7||||4"
msgid "Hey. Y'look like y'just saw a ghost."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||8||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||9||||4"
msgid "Y'did see it, didn't ya? Carryin' a sword."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||10||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah. I actually did more than just see it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||11||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm the gravekeeper 'round these parts.\nStopped by 'cause somethin' felt off tonight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||12||||4"
msgid "Guess that was yer fault."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||13||||4"
msgid "Wait. You've seen the ghost here, too?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||14||||4"
msgid "Y'ain't from here, are ya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||15||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||16||||4"
msgid "Local folks wouldn't dare swing 'round my graveyard.\nEven kids're afraid t'come anywhere near."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||17||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I ain't even heard of an outsider who\nwas brave enough t'show his face in here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||18||||4"
msgid "Huh. I had no idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||19||||4"
msgid "Don't worry 'bout it.\nI ain't tryin' to bring ya down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||20||||4"
msgid "If the legends're true, the ghosts that show up 'round\nhere are pirates who raided the Inland Sea ages ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||21||||4"
msgid "(Pirates...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||22||||4"
msgid "These guys're a real rowdy bunch.\nEven in death, they're always itchin' fer a fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||23||||4"
msgid "If yer feelin' up to it, y'should come\nback and humor 'em sometime."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||24||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||26||||4"
msgid "Pirate ghosts, huh?\nEven in a quiet town like this, I can't catch a break."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||27||||4"
msgid "Something feels off again.\nIt must be the pirate ghosts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||28||||4"
msgid "Long time no see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||29||||4"
msgid "What? There are two of you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||32||||4"
msgid "Ugh, that's enough sleeping on the ground for me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||33||||4"
msgid "I knew ya'd be back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||34||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||35||||4"
msgid "What's yer name, kid?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||36||||4"
msgid "It's Kiryu. Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||37||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, huh? Our spectral buddies're\nreally warmin' up to ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||38||||4"
msgid "And how exactly do you know that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||39||||4"
msgid "I've been watchin' over this place fer years.\nI can tell how they feel."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||40||||4"
msgid "Y'probly can't feel it, but there's a real lively\nenergy flowin' through the air right now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||41||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||42||||4"
msgid "Well it's usually real gloomy 'round here,\nbut it feels like the ghosts're takin' a shine t'ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||43||||4"
msgid "Bet they're jus' lovin' all these fights."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||44||||4"
msgid "This doesn't make much sense."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||45||||4"
msgid "Y'know what? Y'might jus' be the one\nt'finally put their souls t'rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||47||||4"
msgid "The ghosts are here. I can feel it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||48||||4"
msgid "I'm not that interested in fighting you guys."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||49||||4"
msgid "But I've done this much. I'll keep\ngoing until your souls are at peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||50||||4"
msgid "Let's do this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||53||||4"
msgid "Ugh, I wish I didn't pass out every time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||54||||4"
msgid "Hm? It doesn't look like\nthe gravekeeper's coming this time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||55||||4"
msgid "They should be here soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||56||||4"
msgid "So you're still trying to up the ante.\nThink three of you is enough to stop me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||57||||4"
msgid "You guys are quick, but I promise you won't be\ngetting the jump on me any time soon."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||60||||4"
msgid "Every time it's the same thing..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||61||||4"
msgid "So yer back in style, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||62||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||63||||4"
msgid "Thanks t'ya, the fog that's been hangin' over\nthis graveyard's finally startin' t'clear up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||64||||4"
msgid "What do you mean?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||65||||4"
msgid "I reckon it's 'cause yer resolvin' the regrets\nthose ghosts have about their ol' lives."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||66||||4"
msgid "Who exactly are you, old man?\nAre you some kind of psychic?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||67||||4"
msgid "Well, I'm roughly a tenth-generation\ndescendant of the ghosts y'been fightin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||68||||4"
msgid "You're related to them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||69||||4"
msgid "Y'remember how I said they used t'be pirates\nback when they were still alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||70||||4"
msgid "I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||71||||4"
msgid "T'be more precise, they were actually mercenaries\nwho were hired by a big band o' pirates."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||72||||4"
msgid "Go on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||73||||4"
msgid "Back 'round Nobunaga's time, in the 1500s, the pirates\no' Hiroshima got in a real big war with each other."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||74||||4"
msgid "In order t'tip the scales in their favor, one group\no' pirates hired these three legendary mercenaries."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||75||||4"
msgid "Story goes those three coulda taken over the whole\ncountry with jus' a sword if they were feelin' up to it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||76||||4"
msgid "Turns out they didn't really have sea legs, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||77||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||78||||4"
msgid "Got so sick they couldn't even draw their swords.\nThey actually ended up fallin' overboard n' drownin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||79||||4"
msgid "All three of them?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||80||||4"
msgid "Mhm. All at the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||81||||4"
msgid "That's absurd."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||82||||4"
msgid "'Cause their prized mercenaries were gone, the pirates\nwho hired 'em got obliterated by a rival crew."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||84||||4"
msgid "So, the three of 'em died without fully honin'\ntheir skills. 'At's what they're regrettin' now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||85||||4"
msgid "And that's why they're so eager to fight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||86||||4"
msgid "As their descendant, I've been hopin' fer a while now\nthat somebody'd come along n' lay 'em down fer good."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||87||||4"
msgid "'Til that happens, they're jus' gonna\nkeep wanderin' around this graveyard."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||88||||4"
msgid "I gotta say, though... I'm thinkin' y'might be\nthe one who can finally put 'em to rest."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||90||||4"
msgid "Yer probly the only person in the world who's\ngot the raw manpower y'need to do it. So..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||91||||4"
msgid "Jus' one more fight. A final flourish t'let their\nsouls drift into the ether in peace. Please, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||93||||4"
msgid "Our last battle, huh?\nIt'll be sad to say goodbye."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||94||||4"
msgid "It seems like this will be the last time\nI deal with these graveyard ghosts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||95||||4"
msgid "Right, then. They really are ready to end this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||96||||4"
msgid "Hey, can I ask a favor of you guys?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||98||||4"
msgid "I always wake up on the ground after our fights,\nso my clothes get covered in dirt."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||99||||4"
msgid "I was hoping you could help me with that somehow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||100||||4"
msgid "I wonder if they heard me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||103||||4"
msgid "This is... my apartment?\nHow did I get here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||104||||4"
msgid "And what ended up happening to the ghosts?\nI should head over to the graveyard..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||105||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||106||||4"
msgid "Old man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||107||||4"
msgid "Allow me t'thank ya. 'Cause of ya,\nmy ancestors can finally rest in peace."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||108||||4"
msgid "How can you tell, old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||109||||4"
msgid "Trust me, I have my ways."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||110||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||111||||4"
msgid "I've really gotta thank ya fer this. Y'did\nwhat none o' their descendants could ever manage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||112||||4"
msgid "Honestly, I enjoyed going up against them, too.\nIt turned into some pretty decent sparring practice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||113||||4"
msgid "Interestin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||114||||4"
msgid "Y'know, I've always regretted not bein' able t'help\nmy ancestors. Guess ya helped ease my regrets, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||115||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. I'd be honored if ya'd accept this,\nKiryu-san. It's the only way I got t'thank ya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||116||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||117||||4"
msgid "What is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||118||||4"
msgid "It's a talisman t'ward off spirits n' the like.\nY'won't see any more ghosts so long as yer holdin' it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||119||||4"
msgid "That's almost depressing to hear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||120||||4"
msgid "Old man?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||121||||4"
msgid "Does that mean..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||speech_list_sub_b04||table||122||||4"
msgid "Hold on, just what was all of that...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||0||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||1||||4"
msgid "What in the world is this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||3||||4"
msgid "Wh-What the hell!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||4||||4"
msgid "Ah, so that's where Michio-kun's head is.\nFinally found you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||5||||4"
msgid "What was that lazy brat thinking,\nleaving something as special as you out here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||6||||4"
msgid "Hey, what is that thing?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||7||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry. I hope it didn't scare you too much."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||8||||4"
msgid "This little guy is the head of\nour stunning Ono Michio-kun."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||9||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||10||||4"
msgid "Yup! He's an original mascot we're trying to\npromote as the sparkling new face of Onomichi!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||11||||4"
msgid "A mascot...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||12||||4"
msgid "Huh? Do you not know what those are?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||13||||4"
msgid "Well, sort of. Aren't they those cute character\nthings that have been popping up recently?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||14||||4"
msgid "Precisely! These days, they're most commonly\nused as PR to boost local tourism and culture."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||15||||4"
msgid "I'm in a real bind here, though.\nMy usual actor's flown the coop."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||16||||4"
msgid "You have an actor?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||17||||4"
msgid "Of course. A part-timer who donned the guise of\nMichio-kun to spread cheer to the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||18||||4"
msgid "All I did was give him a few pointers.\nKids these days can't take a little criticism."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||19||||4"
msgid "Huh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||20||||4"
msgid "But honestly, we have a big event coming up.\nMichio-kun's supposed to make a dazzling appearance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||21||||4"
msgid "What a mess...\nI'm in hot water without an actor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||22||||4"
msgid "Why don't you do it yourself?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||23||||4"
msgid "No no, I'm all about management.\nI can't act and run the event at the same time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||24||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun's pretty darn big for one of these\nmascots, too. Heavy doesn't begin to describe it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||25||||4"
msgid "I need my actor to be tall and muscular. A wimpy guy\nlike me would never last the whole event."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||26||||4"
msgid "But where could I possibly find someone big and\nstrong enough to handle the role? What a pickle..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||27||||4"
msgid "Hm...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||28||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||29||||4"
msgid "Hmmm!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||30||||4"
msgid "I don't like where this is going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||31||||4"
msgid "I found one!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||32||||4"
msgid "I'm not getting in that thing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||33||||4"
msgid "Come on, please!\nI'll make it up to you somehow!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||34||||4"
msgid "Michio-kun needs someone like you. You're big,\nyou're strong, and you have tons of time on your hands!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||35||||4"
msgid "This really isn't my style."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||36||||4"
msgid "I'm begging you!\nI'll do whatever it takes to get you in there!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||37||||4"
msgid "Besides, there are countless precious little children\nwaiting for Michio-kun's performance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||38||||4"
msgid "Think of their smiling faces.\nYou don't want to leave them disappointed, do you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||39||||4"
msgid "Hm..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||40||||4"
msgid "Please help me!\nYou need to protect their innocent smiles!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||41||||4"
msgid "I'm not really interested in being a mascot...\nWhat should I do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||42||||4"
msgid "Let me think about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||43||||4"
msgid "Okay! I'll be waiting right in\nthis very spot until you're ready!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||44||||4"
msgid "All right, I'll do it.\nJust for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||45||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||46||||4"
msgid "Hey, I'm not Michio yet. The name's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||47||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san! I'm the producer for this event, Hironaka.\nWe're gonna make a great team!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||48||||4"
msgid "Now let's get moving! The sooner we make you\ninto Ono Michio-kun, the better! Come on!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||49||||4"
msgid "Urgh..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||50||||4"
msgid "Won't you please be my mascot actor?\nI'm begging you!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||51||||4"
msgid "Oooh, it's perfect! You're a great fit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||52||||4"
msgid "Hey, do I really have to go through with this?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||53||||4"
msgid "Don't sound so hesitant! It'll be impossible\nto find someone else who suits it so well!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||54||||4"
msgid "It's heavy, though. And hot. And hard to breathe in.\nI can see why your old actor ran off."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||55||||4"
msgid "Cheer up, guy. Ono Michio-kun is the new symbol\nof Onomichi! He's like an idol for these people!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||56||||4"
msgid "What does any of this have to do with Onomichi, anyway?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||57||||4"
msgid "Huh!? You can't tell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||58||||4"
msgid "First up is his charming face, carefully modeled off\nthe local town of Setouchi's specialty hassaku orange!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||59||||4"
msgid "On top of that rests a steamy hat based on\nOnomichi's traditional food, Onomichi ramen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||60||||4"
msgid "Around his waist we have a deliciously fishy pouch\nto show how much this town adores its seafood!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||61||||4"
msgid "And on his feet, cool rubber boots serve\nas a sign of our community's fisherman roots!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||62||||4"
msgid "Finally, Ono Michio-kun's shirt has his name, O-N-O,\nemblazoned on the front in big, bold letters!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||63||||4"
msgid "He's a great representation of our town's beauty.\nDon't you think he's just the perfect little mascot?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||64||||4"
msgid "I don't think I'd go that far..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||65||||4"
msgid "Either way, just be confident! You look amazing,\nKiryu-san! Or should I say, Michio-kun!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||66||||4"
msgid "So, what do you need me to do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||67||||4"
msgid "Oh yeah. The kids will be showing up soon,\nso let's start with a performance! Make it fun for them!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||68||||4"
msgid "But, whatever you do, don't under any\ncircumstances break character!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||69||||4"
msgid "And what character is that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||70||||4"
msgid "Ono Michio-kun is an Onomichi-based fisherman who\nloves the ocean, so he should be as refined as possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||speech_list_sub_b05||table||71||||4"
msgid "This face, refined?"
msgstr ""

